            @{"POSITION/ALIGNMENT/SIZE in the STAGE editor" link "6_1" }, Imagine seems
            to 'forget' what I did!
         2] @{"How do I use the Grow Effect?" link "6_2" }
         3] @{"How do I use the Tumble Effect?" link "6_3" }
         4] How do you get something to @{"roll (at the right speed!)" link "6_4" } while
