        10] @{"Inertia effect: overshoot" link "6_10" }, By Charles Blaquiere and Milan Polle.

    @{fg shine}SECTION 7 - Rendering and the Project Editor@{fg text}
         1] @{"Why do objects render fine in Scan-line, but disappear in Trace?" link "7_1" }
         2] I have a problem with @{"Filtered objects/fog and the Global Backdrop!" link "7_2" }
