            perhaps one transparent glass on a Amiga 3000/25? Is 4.5 hrs
            too much?
         9] @{"Is there any particular format that Imagine prefers?" link "7_9" }
            Ham? 32 Color?  EHB?  24 bit 1000 x 1000?
        10] I would like to use @{"conical light sources" link "7_10" } with my rendering,
            is there anyway "see" in wire-frame where the light will fall?
        11] @{"How important is lighting for a rendering" link "7_11" }, and is there any
            @{"'preset' method" link "7_11" } used to get good results?
        12] @{"Help with Fog" link "7_12" }, How do I use it and how does it work?
        13] @{"How can I render in Wide-screen/Letter-box format?" link "7_13" }
        14] I selected Spheres for my @{"particle object" link "7_14" }, but all I get is a
            polygonal shape!
        15] @{"Help with Fog" link "7_15" }: if you place a fog object inside another,
            they cancel out, why?
        16] The config file says something about '@{"oct-tree level" link "7_16" }'.
            What EXACTLY is this about?

