       20     100
        2      50
        1      20
        0.5    50
        4      20
        0.1     0
        0.4     0

 Column One     Two
       ____    ____
        8     200
        5      50
        5       0
        1     150
        0.5    50
        4      20
        0.1     0
        0.4     0

