         (other settings to 0)

     - Apply Essence Blobf texture:

         Parameter        Value

         Initial scale       120
         # of scalesle       4
         Scale ratio         0.4
         Amplitude ratio     0.4
         Time ratio          0.4
         Time                0
         T1 start            0.2
         T1 end              0.4
         T2 start            0.8
         T2 end              0.96
         Filter red          255
         Filter green        255
         Filter blue         255
         (other settings to default values)


