@endnode

@node "9_3" " SECTION 9 - Miscellaneous "
@{b}@{i} 3] When does one get good enough so that they don't render ugly pictures!@{ub}@{ui}

Practice with a simple objects (to cut down trace time) over and over and over. Varying lighting & color etc. This will allow you to get the effect you want which is only a technical problem.

